---
title: Carb Smart Wonton-Inspired Pork Meatballs with Stir-Fried Veggies
description: This Chinese-inspired dish offers all the delicious flavours of dumplings, but without the wrapper! Minced green onion adds layers of juiciness and flavour to the ground pork mix, while fragrant ginger, broccoli, snap peas and mushrooms tie the dish together.
